{"tid":1154390,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"【誠哥都敢搞】沽空機構GMT指長和(00001)隱瞞577億港元債務 為獲取廉價貸款和高評級","createTime":"2019-05-14T09:15:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-15T03:33:06.000Z","uid":86592,"like":63,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":71,"replies":[{"pid":"07e415b05fec4c1cb5c5d453f8ae9c383baa94ec","tid":1154390,"uid":86592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-14T09:15:30.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.zhitongcaijing.com/content/detail/203680.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.zhitongcaijing.com%2Fcontent%2Fdetail%2F203680.html&d=%2Bo3sOR8bLgAbrAMBqI8fZ%2FS0i%2BS8%2FYHgnNJfWlbrK%2Bw%3D&h=c1e2bea2\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.zhitongcaijing.com/content/detail/203680.html</a><br />\n5月14日，智通財經旗下輿情監測大數據平台&mdash;&mdash;股查查監測到，研究機構GMT Research發佈沽空報告，稱長和(00001)近日發佈的年報顯示，與收購意大利電訊商Wind Tre相關的會計調整，加上2015年重組的殘餘影響，推動其2018財年利潤增加了約132億港元，漲幅達38%。這些非現金調整解釋了為何長和的經營現金流滯後於現金利潤，以及為何資本支出始終超過折舊及攤銷。此外，通過將部分資產視為代售資產，長和可能隱瞞了與代售資產相關的577億港元債務。據推測，這種激進的會計方法正被用來為長和帶來更高的市場評級，以及獲得比原本更廉價的信貸。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/999.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"91433197ca78e5940613cc7d75c7c64d4f6d12ff","tid":1154390,"uid":28195,"like":38,"dislike":9,"score":29,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-14T09:17:42.000Z","msg":"咩GMT Research？未撚聽過"},{"pid":"520a4a2e75aa0ae30d94c06baf33272a4804ffa4","tid":1154390,"uid":63113,"like":33,"dislike":0,"score":33,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-14T09:19:48.000Z","msg":"增持完先搞呢啲嘢<br />\n好古惑"},{"pid":"95b76e6a9dfc736ae46b65fc662ff32b35b625b2","tid":1154390,"uid":118346,"like":28,"dislike":0,"score":28,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-14T09:19:49.000Z","msg":"誠哥大手加持，打爆沽空 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c085262c975b459554d22f0c717d2c1e1ac96092","tid":1154390,"uid":89225,"like":42,"dislike":0,"score":42,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-14T09:28:29.000Z","msg":"別讓李嘉誠跑了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agr